  "text": "As Li et al. suggested in Video object cut and paste [CITATION_1] , other advanced tools like Lazy Snapping [CITATION_2] can also be used for the purpose of key frame segmentation. In our approach which moves only in forward direction of frames, it is sufficient to start with just the first frame as the key frame. During the process, whenever the user desires, the frame can be segmented from scratch and effectively become a key frame.",
